Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't night yet, but with this thick fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's creepy how dark it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of it, we're already\Ncaught in the infamous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Florian Triangle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These seas are haunted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--One appeared!\N--♪ Yo ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ghost ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's the treasure's guardian!\NLet's go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me quite a start!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many decades have passed\Nsince I saw people in the flesh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Joy of Seeing People!\NThe Gentleman Skeleton's True Identity!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Hello, everyone! Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be imposing upon\Nyou here on your vessel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the dead and skeletonized Brook.\NIt's a pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! And what the heck is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my! They're harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, aren't you a lovely lady?\NMay I please see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Harassment Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armed... and... ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:26.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fully decked out in anti-evil stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupid skeleton! B-Beat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil be gone! Evil be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's working! Usopp, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know it! This is my full\N"Anti-Evil Spirit Arsenal."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An evil spirit?! Where? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's you!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! There's no way a skeleton\Ncan walk, talk, and grow an afro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dream! It has to be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew! It's just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! What's up with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he funny? I had him join our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't! I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why you went with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was to keep Luffy from \Ndoing anything crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ashamed of ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on inside! Let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not for you to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you have a splendid\Ndining room! And that kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet it is! It was made\Nby someone as super as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you've got a pretty keen eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't get all chummy with him, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't wait to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had a decent meal in decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had to endure terrible agony every day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the skin on my belly caved\Nin until it touched my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since I'm a skeleton, I don't\Nhave any skin on my belly or back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a skull joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A skull joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a gentleman, I adore the laid-back\Ntime spent while waiting for my meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner, yay! Dinner! C'mon, baby!\N--Food! Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chef! For my drink, I'll take milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Wait quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I forget, Kroobuckle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, actually, you'll have to forgive me,\Nbut I still don't know your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So before I forget, what exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how little do you \Nknow about each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help yourselves. We can\Nkick the skeleton out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, enjoy the meal!\NI used up all the octopi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! Eat all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji's an awesome cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... my heart feels full\Ninstead of my stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you seem to have gotten a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if we swapped plates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's extra, so eat your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw dese octopuses were awive in da\Naquaweeam undil naw too wong ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were alive until just\Nrecently in the aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ship has its own aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bether beweeb it! Fwanky made\Ndis swip and it hash evewyding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is an amazing ship!\NI've never seen one like it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna deck it ow wader?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'd love to take a tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It rocks! Yay! Show it off! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Revive-Revive Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured a Devil Fruit was behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I have already\Ndied once, decades ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe your face first! How'd you\Nmanage to get food all over yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Revive-Revive Fruit lets you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I'm a revived human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It guarantees the mysterious\Npower of a second shot at life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A revived human!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it gave you the power to come\Nback to life once after dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:10:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a long time ago,\NI was a pirate just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fellow pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could beat some manners into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago, my crewmates and I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sailed into the Devil's Sea\Non the ship you saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we had the misfortune of running\Ninto some terribly powerful pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our entire crew was \Nannihilated in the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I died with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was alive, the Revive-Revive's\Nonly power was that I couldn't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on that day, the Fruit's\Npower finally took effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:11:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul returned from the Underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul should have quickly returned\Nto my body, thus reviving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I died on the Devil's Sea and as\Nyou can see, it is dreadfully foggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul wandered through\Nthe fog for an entire year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally managed to find my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by then, it had already turned\Ninto a pearly white skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised that my eyes\Nnearly popped out of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any eyeballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a moron! You're just like Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how you became a talking skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary how the Devil's Fruit\Nstill brought you back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though you're just a skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that the Fruit has done its job,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it just stealing your ability to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's practically a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And skeletons normally\Ndon't have hair, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ever heard of a skeleton with an afro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had strong roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you aren't a ghost?\NYou're actually a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you aren't quite human anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you aren't a ghost, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I hate ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start screaming if I see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hate ghosts? Have you ever\Ntaken a look in the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Please put that mirror away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa! T-Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't the mirror show your reflection?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now that I take a closer look,\Nyou don't have a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! What are you, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't soothe yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're freaking out! And it's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have spent far too many\Nyears drifting on these seas
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to tell my story in one sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story behind why I am a skeleton
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the story behind why I lack a\Nshadow are completely unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain man stole my \Nshadow a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing you move and talk,\Nnothing could surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But does that sorta thing actually happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And having lost my shadow, I am no\Nlonger able to exist in the world of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I cannot live under the light of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only alive now because I avoid the\Nsunlight here on these foggy waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if you\Nwere hit by the sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was directly hit by sunlight, my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was directly hit by sunlight,\Nmy body would be obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obliterated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have witnessed someone who lost his shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ndisappear under the light of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was truly terrifying!\NA hair-raising sight to behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I'm a skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadow appears on the ground\Nwhen you stand in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I lack a shadow,\Nmy body cannot reflect light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I cannot be seen\Nin mirrors or pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the light\Nrejects my very existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my crewmates are all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I've scraped by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scraped down to the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the dead and skeletonized \NBrook. It's a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so cheerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What's wrong? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is truly a wonderful day! I met people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it today or tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On these dark, foggy seas, I can't tell\Nwhen one day moves to the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my crewmates passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all alone on a large ship\Nwith a broken rudder...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I merely rocked on the water\Nas I drifted for several decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lonely! And scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:51.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:18:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad I've lived such a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you as "joy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only my tears hadn't gone dry,\Nso I could shed tears of joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You invited me to join your crew, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That made me truly happy! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm afraid I must turn your offer down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I just explained, my \Nshadow has been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot live under the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently protected by the fog that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nblocks the sunlight here in the Devil's Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I left with you, it would be a matter
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of time before my body was obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stay here and wait
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the miraculous day \Nwhen I reclaim my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like such a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need your shadow, \NI'll take it back for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say someone stole it?\NWho was it? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a really great guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised! However, I cannot tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not ask you to die\Nfor me when we've just met!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning the foe's too strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't kill you! \NAt least give us a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my lips are sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if I'll see him again\Nbefore my second life comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if our paths should ever cross,\NI have decided to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instruments are my pride and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a musician on my pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! You're a musician?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Join my crew, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy a fun sailor song!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G... G-G-G...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! Something's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil be gone! Evil be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's causing that tremor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship was already under observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come look! They've blocked\Nthe path in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what caused that tremor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, did a sea monster gobble us up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the back of the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gate...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look out the aft!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, did you pick up a\Ndrifting barrel while out at sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Offering of Treasure to the Sea God"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's floating on the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:41.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Treasure"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! Maybe a treasure\Nship accidentally dropped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, it opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! That was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been after your ship ever since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ship has been here this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how'd an island get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ghost island \Nthat wanders the seas...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:23:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thriller Bark...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did that skeleton go?\NH-Hey, shouldn't you slow down, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate my navigation technique!\NI'm gonna let her rip!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami, I don't think there's\Nany water over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there--what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"One Unnatural Phenomenon After the Next!\NDisembarking on Thriller Bark!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
